<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full min-h-screen bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 p-8">
  <div class="max-w-4xl w-full space-y-12">
    <div class="text-center space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
        Algorithm <span class="text-blue-500">Visualizer</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Explore the inner workings of classic computer science algorithms through interactive visualizations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all group">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Browse Collection</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Navigate through categories in the sidebar to find Sorting, Pathfinding, and Shuffling algorithms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all group">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-purple-500/20 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Watch & Control</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Control the execution speed, pause, and step through the algorithms to understand every operation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-all group">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Learn Concepts</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
          Gain insights into algorithmic complexity and behavior through visual feedback and descriptions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Available Categories</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-800 rounded text-center text-sm text-slate-300">Sorting</div>
        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-800 rounded text-center text-sm text-slate-300">Pathfinding</div>
        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-800 rounded text-center text-sm text-slate-300">Shuffling</div>
        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-800/50 rounded text-center text-sm text-slate-500 border border-dashed border-slate-700">More coming soon...</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
